OL,3,CMan kicked at police line and shouted
OL,4,C'my country' wrapped in England flag
OL,6,FJohn Kirtley was captured shouting "my
OL,7,Fcountry" during disorder in Sunderland
OL,9,FA man who kicked out at frontline
OL,10,Fofficers and was captured shouting "my
OL,11,Fcountry" while wrapped in an England
OL,12,Fflag has been convicted for his part
OL,13,Fin disorder in Sunderland.
OL,15,FJohn Kirtley, of Rutherglen Road,
OL,16,FSunderland, was remanded in custody
OL,17,Fafter pleading guilty to violent
OL,18,Fdisorder at South Tyneside
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court on Monday (12
OL,20,FAugust).
