OL,6,FThe 26-year-old was identified
OL,7,Ffollowing images and footage shared
OL,8,Fwith police, which included scenes of
OL,9,FKirtley kicking out at frontline
OL,10,Fofficers.
OL,12,FAfter officers issued a public appeal
OL,13,Fto locate Kirtley due to his
OL,14,Finvolvement in the disorder, he handed
OL,15,Fhimself in at Southwick police station
OL,16,Fon Sunday.
