OL,3,CMan kicked at police line and shouted
OL,4,C'my country' wrapped in England flag
OL,6,FThe defendant was among three men to
OL,7,Fbe convicted over their roles in the
OL,8,Fdisorder in the city, which erupted on
OL,9,FFriday 2 August - the week that three
OL,10,Fgirls died in a mass stabbing in
OL,11,FSouthport, Merseyside.
OL,13,FJack Fowler, 24, of Beaumont Terrace,
OL,14,FNewcastle, also appeared before
OL,15,Fmagistrates in South Tyneside
OL,16,Fyesterday on Monday.
OL,18,FHe admitted one charge of violent
OL,19,Fdisorder and was remanded in custody
OL,20,Funtil his sentencing at Newcastle
OL,21,FCrown Court on 23 August.
