OL,6,FKirtley will be sentenced on 22 August.
OL,8,FJames Aspin, 34, of Briardale Road,
OL,9,FBlyth, appeared before magistrates in
OL,10,FBedlington on Monday charged with one
OL,11,Fcount of distributing a recording to
OL,12,Fstir religious hatred.
OL,14,FPolice were made aware of content
OL,15,Fposted by Aspin last Friday gaining
OL,16,Ftraction across TikTok ` making
OL,17,Fhateful and threatening comments.
OL,19,FHe was arrested in the early hours of
OL,20,Fthe Saturday morning, after being
OL,21,Frecognised by officers.
